text: Reignfall is the third extended play by American rapper Chamillionaire. It was released on July 23, 2013.Reignfall release date on chamillionaire.com | July 23, 3013 ==Track listing== ==Charts== Reignfall was Chamillionaires first project since his second studio album Ultimate Victory to chart on a Billboard chart.
